==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overplus
<hw>O"ver*plus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Over</ets> +
L. <ets>plus</ets> more. See <er>Plus</er>, and cf.
<er>Surplus</er>.]</ety> <def>That which remains after a supply, or
beyond a quantity proposed; surplus.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>overplus</xex> of a great fortune.⟦rdquo⟧
<au>Addison.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overply</ent>⟦br⟧
